column3:
Ulysses: Did you see your grades?
Peter: Yes. 
Ulysses: I got an A
Peter: Me too
Julia: B
Martha: Where can I check them?
Julia: Online
Julia: On the course page
column4: Ulysses and Peter got A's, Julia got B. Martha wants to check her grades, too.
